    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>看了网上各种教程，都说很简单，我捣鼓了3天才整出来。
期间遇到各种网上都找不到答案的问题，在此记录下过程，以便参考。</p>

<p>由于刚接触，Markdown语法也不是很清楚，估计写完排版会很丑。。</p>

<p>看到此教程，应该是对Github和Octopress有个大概的了解了，详
细的介绍自己百度（最近Google又上不去了？不喜欢翻墙）。</p>

<p>下面开始，一步一步来应该是没有问题的。</p>

<!--more-->


<h2>一、本地环境搭建（Win7 32位系统）</h2>

<h3>1.安装Git</h3>

<p>windows 环境下安装 Git，百度 msysgit 自行下载，一步步Next即可。。</p>

<h3>2.安装Ruby</h3>

<p>一般推荐的版本Ruby1.9.3以上，安装时勾选 Add Ruby executables to your PATH。
将Ruby加入系统环境变量，完成后打开cmd执行：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">ruby</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">v</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>输出版本号表示成功。</p>

<h3>3.安装DevKit</h3>

<p>下载完成，解压即可。这里以解压到F:\DevKit为例，
打开cmd执行</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="ss">F</span><span class="p">:</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">cd</span> <span class="no">DevKit</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">ruby</span> <span class="n">dk</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rb</span> <span class="n">init</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">ruby</span> <span class="n">dk</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rb</span> <span class="n">install</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>4.配置Windows系统环境变量</h3>

<p>为了支持UTF-8编码，开始-计算机-属性-高级系统设置，添加两个变量，LANG和LC_ALL，值都是 zh_CN.UTF-8</p>

<h3>5.更换Ruby更新源</h3>

<p>有人说更新比较慢，我的没更换感觉也挺快的，打开cmd，执行：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">gem</span> <span class="n">sources</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">a</span> <span class="ss">http</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="sr">//</span><span class="n">ruby</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">taobao</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">org</span><span class="o">/</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">gem</span> <span class="n">sources</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">r</span> <span class="ss">http</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="sr">//</span><span class="n">rubygems</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">org</span><span class="o">/</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>环境基本上就搭好了，下面开始搭建博客。。</p>

<h2>二、搭建博客系统</h2>

<h3>1.克隆Octopress库</h3>

<p>找一个存放Octopress的目录，打开Git Bash（右键鼠标应该可以看到），执行：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">git</span> <span class="nb">clone</span> <span class="ss">git</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="sr">//</span><span class="n">github</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">com</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">imathis</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">octopress</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">git</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>完成之后，执行：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">cd</span> <span class="n">octopress</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">gem</span> <span class="n">install</span> <span class="n">bundler</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">bundle</span> <span class="n">install</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p></p>

<h3>2.创建Github Repository</h3>

<p>没有Github得先注册帐号，验证邮箱，之后New Repository ，注意：
Repository name 必须是 your_username.github.io (这里your_username替换成你自己的
帐号，以前的可能是 your_username.github.com ， 现在官方推荐 your_username.github.io ）
下面选项默认即可，点击 Create Repository 之后 ，什么都不要做了。</p>

<h3>3.设置 SSH keys</h3>

<p>绑定Github与本地电脑，不用每次都输入用户名密码，如果不设置，后面可能出现错误。
首先，本地创建一个SSH key ， 打开cmd执行：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">ssh</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">keygen</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">t</span> <span class="n">rsa</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">C</span><span class="s2">&quot;your_email@your_email.com&quot;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>（就是你的邮箱啊）
按照提示输入即可。完成之后，到c:\Users\用户名.ssh\目录找到id_rsa.pub，并用文本编辑打开复制全部。</p>

<p>然后，到github网站右上角点击“Account settings”>>“SSH Keys”>>“Add SSH key”，将刚才复制的内容粘贴
到key文本框内，Title任意。</p>

<p>最后，测试一下。打开cmd执行：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">ssh</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">T</span> <span class="n">git</span><span class="vi">@github</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">com</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>4.设置个人信息</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">config</span> <span class="o">--</span><span class="n">global</span> <span class="n">user</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">name</span> <span class="s2">&quot;your_username&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">config</span> <span class="o">--</span><span class="n">global</span> <span class="n">user</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">email</span> <span class="s2">&quot;your_email@your_email.com&quot;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>请自行替换 your_username 为 你注册的帐号，替换 <a href="&#x6d;&#97;&#x69;&#x6c;&#116;&#x6f;&#58;&#121;&#x6f;&#117;&#114;&#x5f;&#x65;&#109;&#x61;&#x69;&#x6c;&#x40;&#121;&#x6f;&#117;&#x72;&#x5f;&#x65;&#109;&#x61;&#x69;&#x6c;&#x2e;&#99;&#111;&#109;">&#121;&#111;&#117;&#x72;&#95;&#x65;&#109;&#97;&#105;&#x6c;&#x40;&#x79;&#111;&#117;&#x72;&#x5f;&#101;&#109;&#97;&#x69;&#108;&#x2e;&#x63;&#111;&#109;</a>
为 你验证的邮箱。</p>

<h2>三、发布博客到Github</h2>

<h3>1.创建Github Pages</h3>

<p>打开Git Bash，进入octopress目录，执行：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">rake</span> <span class="n">setup_github_pages</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>根据提示输入Repository Url：git@github.com:your_username/your_username.github.io.git
自行替换 your_username</p>

<p>注意：这一步出现的问题，①找不到Repository，检查输入的Url或Github创建的仓库是否正确；
②访问被拒绝，检查是否设置SSH keys。</p>

<h3>2.安装Octopress主题</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">rake</span> <span class="n">install</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>这是安装默认主题，也可以克隆其他主题。</p>

<h3>3.生成静态页面</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">rake</span> <span class="n">generate</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>4.本地预览</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">rake</span> <span class="n">preview</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>在浏览器输入地址：<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a>
打开本地预览，也可跳过预览。
Ctrl + C 停止预览</p>

<h3>5.提交到Github</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">rake</span> <span class="n">deploy</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>提交_deploy里的文件到Github的master分支，source分支默认不提交。</p>

<p>注意：这一步出现的问题，提交失败，一般是仓库的版本号跟本地的不一致，
解决办法：先，git pull ，再 git push ，但是这个问题困扰我2天，终于找到
原因了。
原来，我把 Repository 克隆了一份在本地，而Octopress中_deploy中也是master
分支，两个冲突了，按照此教程则不会出现此问题。</p>

<p>这时候，在浏览器中输入 <a href="http://your_username.github.io">http://your_username.github.io</a> 自行替换 your_username
会看到404页面，第一次提交需要10分钟左右时间，等吧，我等了一个周末，周一发现
终于出来了。。</p>

<h3>6.提交源代码</h3>

<p>Github本来就是源代码管理的，提交source分支</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">add</span> <span class="o">.</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">commit</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">m</span> <span class="s2">&quot;your tag&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">push</span> <span class="n">origin</span> <span class="n">source</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>四、配置博客</h2>

<h3>1.设置中文编码</h3>

<p>如果博客中有中文，需要修改编码格式
打开F:\Ruby193\lib\ruby\gems\1.9.1\gems\jekyll-2.0.3\lib\jekyll\convertible.rb
修改46行上下为下面的样子：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='js'><span class='line'> <span class="nx">begin</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nx">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">content</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">File</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">read</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">File</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">join</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">base</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="nx">name</span><span class="p">),</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="nx">encoding</span><span class="o">=&gt;</span><span class="s2">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="nx">content</span> <span class="o">=~</span> <span class="sr">/\A(---\s*\n.*?\n?)^((---|\.\.\.)\s*$\n?)/m</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="nx">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">content</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">$POSTMATCH</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="nx">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">SafeYAML</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">load</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">$1</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nx">end</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>   <br/>
有的版本还需要改别的地方，视情况而改。。</p>

<h3>2.新建博文</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">rake</span> <span class="n">new_post</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;your bolg title&#39;</span><span class="o">]</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>这样在_posts文件夹下建立一个.markdown后缀的文件，文本编辑器打开可以改标题，
写内容，语法自行学习，兼容html语法，我基本没用语法，就成这个样子了。</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="n">rake</span> <span class="n">generate</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">rake</span> <span class="n">deploy</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>3.添加评论功能</h3>

<p>Octopress自带disqus评论系统，一般国内用的比较多的是多说<a href="http://duoshuo.com/">http://duoshuo.com/</a>
获取代码 如下：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
<span class='line-number'>18</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='js'><span class='line'><span class="c">&lt;!--</span> <span class="err">多说评论框</span> <span class="nx">start</span> <span class="o">--&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nx">div</span> <span class="kr">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;ds-thread&quot;</span> <span class="nx">data</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">thread</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">key</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;唯一ID自己定义&quot;</span> <span class="nx">data</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">title</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot; 文章标题&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nx">data</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">url</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;文章Url&quot;</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="err">/div&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c">&lt;!--</span> <span class="err">多说评论框</span> <span class="nx">end</span> <span class="o">--&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c">&lt;!--</span> <span class="err">多说公共</span><span class="nx">JS</span><span class="err">代码</span> <span class="nx">start</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="err">一个网页只需插入一次</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">--&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nx">script</span> <span class="nx">type</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;text/javascript&quot;</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">duoshuoQuery</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="nx">short_name</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="s2">&quot;your_short_name&quot;</span><span class="p">};</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="p">(</span><span class="kd">function</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">ds</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">createElement</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;script&#39;</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="nx">ds</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">type</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">&#39;text/javascript&#39;</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="nx">ds</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">async</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="p">;</span>
